videos.description: Frank Howard inbounds the ball to Marek Dolezaj, who gives it right back to Howard for the 1-handed throwdown.
videos.headline: Syracuse with 1-handed jam off of inbounds pass

videos.description: Will Rayman takes the steal and goes all the way to the bucket and finishes with the circus layup while collecting the foul.
videos.headline: Colgate with a circus layup
